text: Quilmes Airport (, ) is a public use airport serving Quilmes, a suburb of Buenos Aires, Argentina. The Ezeiza VOR-DME (Ident: EZE) is west-southwest of the airport. The Quilmes non-directional beacon (Ident: ILM) is located on the field. == References == Category:Airports in Argentina Category:Buildings and structures in Buenos Aires
